text:
I nearly had a complete nervous breakdown in the last 15 minutes… We were five minutes away from Calder's dentist appointment, I was getting everything in the car, and Mira had a massive blowout that went through all of her clothes into her chair and all the way down my outfit… I brought her upstairs to get her changed and to clean myself and get changed… 
And Calder was upset from the lack of attention and went into the garage and grabbed ski poles… Which he proceeded to bring up to the bedroom and hit everything in the room with as hard as physically possible… 

Until I took him away- arms covered in poop - at which point he decided to overturn Aaron's basket full of miscellaneous items by the bathroom… the smash noise freaked Mira who started screaming - And then take his magnetic toys and throw them everywhere in the room screaming… scaring her more...
at which point I was soaking her clothes, washing her down, so I took a break to yell at him, and he punched me in the face ... 

We are at the dentist now. 15m late. Clean outfits. But I'm just mentally done.
